1. "On je poludeo* kada je čuo da joj se dogodi tako nešto." (He went crazy when he heard that something like that happened to her.)
2. "Čim je ona otišla, on polu*deo." (As soon as she left, he went mad.)
3. "Čim je čuo da je umro, polude*o je." (As soon as he heard that he died, he went crazy.)
4. "Ona je poluda*la od straha." (She went mad from fear.)
5. "Svi su poludeli* kada je on izašao iz zatvora." (Everyone went crazy when he came out of prison.)